Molim te, molim te.

321
00:49:39,881 --> 00:49:41,881
Šta to radiš?

322
00:49:53,227 --> 00:49:59,464
Džone? To si bio ti? Zašto?

323
00:49:59,834 --> 00:50:01,834
Zašto smo ovde?

324
00:50:02,637 --> 00:50:08,475
Džone! Šta je ovo?
